<p>I need to <strong>grep AND three patterns</strong> in multiple files , I found I way to grep AND two patterns in multiple file  {grep -E 'pattern1.*pattern2' *} for example ,I  have two files </p>  <ol> <li><p>File1 contain</p>  <p>1 ,2 ,3</p>  <p>4 ,5</p></li> <li><p>File2 contain</p>  <p>1,2,3</p>  <p>4</p></li> </ol>  <p>I need to grep the file the contain 1 and 3 and 5 </p>